OOC: Good to have you back Jason.  I enjoyed RPing your chars.  Arcangel is 
in the middle of the battle with the Trainers at the Ark(which is destroyed), 
but the battle is pretty much over and theres a standstilll, with a bunch of 
Kingler's characters talking about fixing the ark and peace.  Tigerhawk is in 
the CF at the mess hall having a drink with Airazor, and Depth Charge is 
where you left him. Trinity has discovered that her parents are dead, and 
Aerotaur is going to take care of her.
